results.title: Infinity Gauntlet (1991) #1
results.description:
Seeking to impress the Mistress Death, who returned him to life, Thanos
has gained control over the Infinity Gauntlet -- making him an
all-powerful god! With Mephisto as his familiar, Thanos wipes out half
of the life in the universe with a snap of his fingers! What will Earth
do when half its the heroes are killed?

textObjects.text:
Seeking to impress the Mistress Death, who returned him to life, Thanos
has gained control over the Infinity Gauntlet -- making him an
all-powerful god! With Mephisto as his familiar, Thanos wipes out half
of the life in the universe with a snap of his fingers! What will Earth
do when half its the heroes are killed?
One of the most epic Marvel stories ever told deserves a cover that does it justice.  George Perez delivers in spades.
